@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_jcdgwp(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = wp.cos((wp.abs(tmp + 0.52) / (tmp + 0.83 - v0 + 0.95)))
    v0 = wp.abs(0.46)
    v1 = wp.cos((v0 + v0))
    v0 = wp.sin(v2)
    data[tid] = v0
